      "id": "PopularPost142491",
      "post_content": "this card is really amazing as far as how versatile it is and how it STILL manages to almost not be broken. Unfortunately, Consecrated Sphinx breaks this in so many ways, I'd be surprised if he doesnt show his ugly face in a Legacy or Vintage match soon.\n  \nI wonder if they could make an updated card 'counter target spell, its controller draws 1 card' ?\n  \nthat would be less powerful, but still in keeping with the spell's purpose. ",
