      "post_content": "This is my counter-counterspell spell.  \n  \nAun gets it right. Arcane Denial turns any spell in your hand into [Ancestral Recall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ancestral Recall) for the low low price of ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol). Run four, and you'll feel more comfortable running a low-cc card in your deck that's only useful some of the time.",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
