      "post_content": "Counterspell one of your own spells in order to draw 3 cards... and put a card from your hand into your graveyard. There are plenty of decks that benefit from having specific cards in their graveyard, and even more that can bypass it. (Like [Bloodghast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodghast)).",
