    {
      "id": "PopularPost299877",
      "post_content": "This card is one of the rare gems of Magic. It is a card whose power is subtle, and most people miss it on first look. Even people I have wasted with this card don't understand how such a seemingly disadvantageous card can wreak so much havoc.  \n  \nIt is a hard counter for 1U. Think about that for a minute. Nearly any spell, poof, gone, and it is very splashable. Not only is it a hard counter, but it replaces itself. [Dismiss](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dismiss) costs twice the mana. And the disadvantage? You're running blue! [Arcane laboratory](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arcane laboratory), more counterspells, run it with black for discard and you have more food for your [megrim](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=megrim) or [lilliana's caress](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lilliana's caress). Run it with mill. Run it with weenie and they might never get the chance to use those cards.",
      "posted_by": "voidweaver",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost299877\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">This card is one of the rare gems of Magic.  It is a card whose power is subtle, and most people miss it on first look. Even people I have wasted with this card don't understand how such a seemingly disadvantageous card can wreak so much havoc.<br/><br/>It is a hard counter for 1U.  Think about that for a minute.  Nearly any spell, poof, gone, and it is very splashable.  Not only is it a hard counter, but it replaces itself.  <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dismiss\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dismiss\">Dismiss</a> costs twice the mana.  And the disadvantage?  You're running blue!  <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Arcane laboratory\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arcane laboratory\">Arcane laboratory</a>, more counterspells, run it with black for discard and you have more food for your <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"megrim\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=megrim\">megrim</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"lilliana's caress\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lilliana's caress\">lilliana's caress</a>.  Run it with mill.  Run it with weenie and they might never get the chance to use those cards.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '299877'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy84869\">voidweaver</span>\r\n                                (2/13/2013 8:28:46 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
